description.short: A full-stack job seeking / posting platform built with Shopify Polaris and React.js in a team environment. The app has authentication, authorization, CRUD, search and filtering functionalities.
This is a minimal full-stack todo app that has all of the CRUD operations, plus authentication and authorization. The passwords of users are also salted and hashed before being hosted on Database.
This is a food and resturant explorer Android app built with React Native, which uses Yelp's APIs to get the details of the resturants.
This is a mock portfolio website purely done to practice HTML and CSS to build a responsive website that just works - it even has its own address bar theme on Chrome for Android!
Part of the concept for a social media app, done purely for fun and in my spare time, built with just Microsoft Office PowerPoint.
A VR simulation for an architectural project built with Unreal Engine and very economic and accessible equipments.
UI and UX of an MVP desktop app me and my team designed along with its business model at a Startup Weekend event.
